# SDD Intake Checklist

- Confirm source document path/version.
- Extract atomic requirements as `REQ-###`.
- Separate functional and non-functional requirements.
- Group by bounded context and dependency direction.
- Detect cross-cutting controls (security, observability, reliability, operability).
- Flag unresolved inputs as `BLOCKED_MISSING_INPUTS`.
- Keep each spec at `SPEC_READY=false` until blockers are resolved.
